      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Tricore and SCR is connected with 8Kb of XRAM"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In which 4Kb is used for CODE and 4Kb is used for DATA (in which 128 bytes is used a shared RAM between Tricore and SCR)"
    },
